  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Each child under the age of one year that was referred for 24h pH-MII monitoring to
             exclude pathological gastro-oesophageal reflux (GOR)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  : prematurity (gestational age less than 37 weeks), the use of anti-reflux medication
             and reflux surgery (Nissen fundoplication)
      </textblock>
